Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:42.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}双峰\N第三季 第十二集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:50.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地戈登在他的酒窖里储备了刨子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank God Gordon stocks the plane from his own wine cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:53.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  你去告诉她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, you'll be the one to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:58.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,别理会这个怪人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ignore the strange man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:07.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,-敬联调局  -敬联调局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Here's to the bureau. - To the bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:08.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,敬联调局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To the bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:17.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:19.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,戈登\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:25.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  现在说说你需要知道的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, here's what you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:29.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,拜托说得简洁点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please speak succinctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:34.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,别发出任何尖锐的噪音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and do not make any loud, sharp noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:45.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,1970年  美国空军终止了蓝皮书计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In 1970, the United States Air Force shut down Project Blue Book,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:48.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,即他们对不明飞行物为期二十年的调查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}their 20-year investigation into UFOs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:52.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们得出结论  没有可靠证据存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They concluded that no credible evidence existed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:55.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,因此他们认为不明飞行物对国家安全没有威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and therefore they posed no threat to national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,换句话说  是个巨大的掩饰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In other words, a massive cover-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:02:59.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,干杯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:02.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,干杯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:12.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,几年后  军方和联调局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A few years later, the military and FBI
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:14.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,组建了一支高度机密的特遣部队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}formed a top secret task force
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:16.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,去探索蓝皮书没能解答的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to explore the troubling abstractions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:19.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,令人不安的抽象概念\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}raised by cases Blue Book failed to resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:22.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们称之为蓝色玫瑰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We called it the Blue Rose after a phrase
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:24.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是那些案件中的一个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}uttered by a woman in one of these cases
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,临死前说出的一个词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just before she died
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,暗示着我们永远无法企及这些答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which suggested these answers could not be reached
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:32.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,除非通过我们从未踏足过的另一条途径\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}except by an alternate path we've been traveling ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:36.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,戈登推荐了一位名叫菲利普·杰弗里斯的探员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gordon suggested an agent by the name of Phillip Jeffries
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,作为队长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to head the squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:39.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,他很快招募了另外三人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He soon recruited three others:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:42.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我  切特·戴斯蒙德和戴尔·库柏  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}myself, Chet Desmond, and Dale Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许你已经注意到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Perhaps you haven't failed to notice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:46.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是那组人里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that I'm the only one of that group
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,唯一没有无故消失的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who hasn't disappeared without explanation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以戈登也迟迟没有向我们团队中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which has led to a certain reluctance on Gordon's part
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,注入新鲜的血液\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to bring new blood into the fold...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:56.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,直至今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}until tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:02.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,普雷斯顿探员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Agent Preston,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:04.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们关注你很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you've been on our radar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:07.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在华盛顿高中上了荣誉榜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}since you made the honors list at George Washington High,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:09.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是麻省理工的年度优秀学生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}not to mention the dean's list at MIT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:12.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,并在匡提科名列前茅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and top of your class at Quantico.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:22.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们想让我加入蓝色玫瑰特遣队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're asking me to join the Blue Rose task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,我加入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:37.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,明早我跟你简单介绍具体情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll brief you in detail in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:39.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,敬塔米和蓝色玫瑰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To Tammy and the Blue Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:54.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,敬蓝色玫瑰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Blue Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:56.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,敬蓝色玫瑰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Blue Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:28.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,戴安在路上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Diane's on her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,请坐 戴安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have a seat, Diane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,喝一杯吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Care for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:55.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢冰镇的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I like it on the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,你运气好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, you're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:01.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,达科他还是冰天雪地的季节\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Dakotas are still in the Ice Age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,戴安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Diane,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:39.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们你知道你跟库柏探员的合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we know your work with Agent Cooper has given you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:42.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,让你对蓝色玫瑰有了较深了解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}more than a passing insight into the Blue Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:44.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,即便你已经不是局里的人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Even though you're no longer a part of the bureau,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是想当你的代理人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we'd like to deputize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,只是暂时的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On a temporary basis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:50.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们真的需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because we really need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我有什么好处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's in it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:00.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,现金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,不太多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,或许还有查清你朋友库柏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe the satisfaction of learning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,究竟遭遇了什么的满足感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what happened to your friend Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:31.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,那就开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:52.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,能给我一盒塞勒姆香波吗  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, could I have a carton of Salems, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}牛肉干
