Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:32.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不这么认为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh. I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:35.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,自从我拒绝再给他钱后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We pretty much lost contact
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们就基本上没联系了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when I refused to give him more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:41.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,哈里怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,还撑得住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's hanging in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:46.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然  我们还是保持乐观\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Course, we're hoping for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:48.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:50.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个女孩呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:51.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,她在这里的医院吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is she in the hospital here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,在重症监护病房里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Intensive care?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:56.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:01.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,那那个小男孩的父母呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the boy's parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:05.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,可想而知吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As you can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:23.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我准备把这个寄给哈里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was going to send this to Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:25.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:27.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,这把钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The key here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:31.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,前几天随着邮件寄给我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Showed up in the mail the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:37.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们近二十年来都没用过这种钥匙了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We haven't used a key like this in over 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:42.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,315房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Room 315.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:47.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很肯定这就是库柏特工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm pretty sure that this is the key
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:49.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,原来住的房间的钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to Agent Cooper's old room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:55.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得哈里会想留个纪念\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought Harry would like to have it as a memento.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他会吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You think he would?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:00.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:03.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,会的  本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:06.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想我把这个带给他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want me to take it for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:09.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:11.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:13.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他会喜欢吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You think he would like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:15.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:18.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,很有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:23.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们正好有个新案子和库柏特工有关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're just opening up an old case involving Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:26.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:30.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,过了这么多年这把钥匙突然冒了出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}this key shows up after all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:34.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:37.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也这么觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.12,0:21:44.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我真的觉得他会喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I really think he would like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:46.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,这会对他很有意义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It'd mean a lot to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.73,0:21:54.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  本  给你带来了这样一个坏消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry, Ben, to bring you this news.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:56.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴再见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:21:59.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,真希望不是因为这种事来找你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wish it was under better circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:01.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:05.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果有他的消息  我会告诉你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll let you know if, uh... if I hear from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:09.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们有了新进展也会通知你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll let you know if we have more news.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.38,0:22:14.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:19.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,给哈里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:51.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,理查德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Richard,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:54.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的孙子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}my grandson,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:22:59.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,杀死了那个小男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}killed that little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,0:23:05.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.08,0:23:17.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,理查德生下来就没有父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Richard never had a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:31.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我记得...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.23,0:23:34.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我记得怎么骑自行车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I remember riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.65,0:23:42.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲给了我一辆旧施文自行车...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My father got me this old Schwinn...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:45.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,二手的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...secondhand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.33,0:23:49.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,他把它漆成了绿色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He painted it green,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.16,0:23:53.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,安了一个新坐板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}got a new seat for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,两种绿色  有点儿...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Two-tone green, kind of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.67,0:24:02.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,柠檬绿和深丛林绿混在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}kind of a lime green and a deep forest green.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.38,0:24:06.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,轮胎很大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fat tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.36,0:24:10.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,好难骑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, it was so hard to ride,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.97,0:24:13.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我很喜欢那辆自行车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I loved that bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.63,0:24:19.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢那辆自行车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I loved that bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.44,0:24:25.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我和我的朋友一起骑自行车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd ride with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.40,0:24:38.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,打给医院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Call the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.74,0:24:42.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,把她的费用都结清了  米里亚姆...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want you to arrange to pay for all of Miriam, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.90,0:24:45.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我记不清她姓什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't even remember her last name,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.59,0:24:47.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,但他们会知道是谁的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but they'll-they'll know who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.33,0:24:50.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,米里亚姆的所有医疗费用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All of Miriam's medical expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.40,0:24:54.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,理查德袭击了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Richard assaulted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.97,0:24:58.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,她需要做手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She needs an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.65,0:25:01.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,贝弗莉  请马上去办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Beverly, please take care of this right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.48,0:25:02.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,好  没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.41,0:25:04.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,我马上去办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll do it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.15,0:25:16.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我特别喜欢那辆自行车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I loved that bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.88,0:25:21.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢那辆自行车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I loved that bike
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.66,0:25:25.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是我父亲送给我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that my father got for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.66,0:25:32.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,陷阱已经布好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The trap was set.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.01,0:25:35.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们等待着午夜过后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They waited till after midnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.72,0:25:40.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后75名壮汉翻过这座山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then, 75 strong, they came up over the mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.02,0:25:43.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,警笛哀嚎  拔枪布阵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}sirens wailing, guns drawn--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.96,0:26:03.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.99,0:26:15.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,戈登\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gordon,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.49,0:26:18.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能要你的朋友到楼下等候吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}would you please ask your friend to wait downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.55,0:26:25.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  你能让我们单独待会儿吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sweetheart, would you excuse us for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.10,0:26:27.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我到酒吧打给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll call you in the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.90,0:26:31.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oui, mon chéri.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.71,0:27:10.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,很别致\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Très chic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.21,0:28:02.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,太好喝了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Très bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.01,0:28:05.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是好酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.76,0:29:02.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,到了酒吧打给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Call you at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.39,0:29:13.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,她来这拜访一位她母亲的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's here visiting a friend of her mother
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.46,0:29:15.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,她女儿失踪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}whose daughter has gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.95,0:29:19.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,她拥有一座萝卜地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The mother owns a turnip farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.85,0:29:21.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要她告诉那位母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I told her to tell the mother
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.74,0:29:25.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,她女儿最后会出现的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that her daughter will turn up eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.74,0:29:35.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,她也没听懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She didn't get it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.62,0:29:38.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,她是法国人  语言不通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Being French, it doesn't translate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.46,0:29:40.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,你明白了吗  艾伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you realize, Albert,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.63,0:29:45.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,如今地球上有超过六千种语言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that there are more than 6,000 languages spoken on Earth today?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.93,0:29:59.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么事  艾伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is it, Albert?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.56,0:30:06.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,戴安收到了这样的短信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Incoming to Diane:
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.15,0:30:08.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,"拉斯维加斯吗"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Las Vegas?"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.79,0:30:13.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,她回道"他们还没说"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Outgoing: "They haven't asked yet."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.00,0:30:24.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有什么没有跟她说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do we know that we haven't asked her about?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.13,0:30:34.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,会知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.21,0:30:37.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,但目前  我真的很想继续享用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But for now, I'd really like to get back to
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.01,0:30:39.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,这瓶上等的波尔多葡萄酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}this fine Bordeaux.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.82,0:30:42.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What kind is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.09,0:30:48.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,11点05分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}1105.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.88,0:31:14.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Albert...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.23,0:31:21.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有时候真令我担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...sometimes I really worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.51,0:32:04.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.63,0:32:06.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,我确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.31,0:32:09.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,没时间折磨他了  宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We don't have time for torture, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.87,0:32:11.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我饿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.59,0:32:13.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚路过一家温迪汉堡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Passed a Wendy's back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.53,0:32:15.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,开枪打死他就对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.04,0:32:17.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,好  没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, I'm there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.97,0:32:21.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我可以打他的腿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can shoot him in the legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.73,0:32:22.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,咱们绑架他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We kidnap him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.90,0:32:24.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样你就能折磨他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then you could torture him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.63,0:32:28.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说过  我饿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Told you, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.52,0:32:30.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就确认一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just making sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.22,0:32:43.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,他来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's here.
